<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/713702-why-does-max-lucado-say-the-most-repeated">Why does Max Lucado say &quot;the most repeated command from the lips of Jesus was &#39;Fear not&#39;? Jesus&#39; most repeated command was LOVE! I count 38 times in the four gospels Jesus tells us to love and find the words &quot;fear not&quot; only 11 times. And about half of those times, the command wasn&#39;t from Jesus but from an angel of the Lord.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_713702'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F281520.In_the_Grip_of_Grace">like</a></span>

</li>
