<a href="/questions/712395-max-lucado-says-in-chapter-10-that-every">Max Lucado says in Chapter 10 that &quot;every book in the Bible&quot; contains the words &quot;fear not.&quot; I don&#39;t believe this is true. I don&#39;t think they are in Esther or Malachi and probably a lot of the other books as well. Can anybody tell me where those words appear in every book?</a>
