<span id="freeTextContainer4944964911774756328"><strong>Everyone needs to read this book</strong><br/><br/>Everyone needs to read this book. If you have questions about if you have lived a life too far away from God and that he will not accept you, read this book. If you say you are a believer but still doing good things to be in his good graces, read this book. If you are new learning about what it means to be a Christian, read this book. It’s an eye opener!</span>

