              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3570383027854039804">Amazing! Max Lucado journeys with us through the book of Romans. If you don’t know Jesus, read this book. If you know Jesus, read this book. Grace is the greatest gift you will ever receive. You are God’s creation and He loves you. It is His sacrifice which reconciles us to Him. How do choose? What kind of person are you? What do you believe? Read this book!</span>

          </span>
